Clementine
Dark Chocolate Chips
Sea Salt Flakes

Peel the clementines and separate each individual orange segment

In a microwave-safe small bowl, melt the chocolate chips in a microwave for 1-2 min.

Dip half of each orange segment into the chocolate, then lay it on a parchment-lined baking sheet.

Dip half of each orange segment into the chocolate, then lay it on a parchment-lined baking sheet.

Place the baking sheet in the refrigerator until the chocolate is firm, 10-15 min.

Transfer to a platter.